Apa yang terjadi?

306
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:41,030
Tunggu.
Akan kulepaskan.

307
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:55,460
Maaf telah meninggalkanmu sendiri.

308
00:17:55,690 --> 00:17:56,540
Eh?

309
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,600
