344
00:20:02,460 --> 00:20:05,390
Takemichi pasti berhasil!

345
00:20:09,270 --> 00:20:11,260
Aku payah banget, ya.

346
00:20:11,740 --> 00:20:13,440
Jangan menangis lagi, ya.

347
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:15,470
Aku enggak 'nangis.
