350
00:20:22,740 --> 00:20:23,690
Oke.

351
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,120
Kali ini,

352
00:20:30,170 --> 00:20:32,120
aku akan menghentikan Bang Kiyomasa!

353
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:34,030
Lalu ....

354
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:38,320
Aku akan mengakhiri traumaku
dan diriku yang selalu melarikan diri!

355
00:20:43,060 --> 00:20:44,160
Takemicchi?

356
00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:45,420
Bang Mitsuya?

357
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,360
Loh, kau sendirian?

358
00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:48,700
